{"tid":2435155,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指欺凌員工！哈利Meghan與王室決裂：「既然王室散播謠言，不要妄想我們沉默」","createTime":"2021-03-06T04:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T18:42:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc483e8038d85c33c69dc22395bd163f9b934883","tid":2435155,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.aQwXhhRfoxcH57l5haazA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxOS42OTUwNDQ0NzI2ODE-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/C6kbRyAt1XpOAzSFF9JKKw--~B/aD01OTA7dz03ODc7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/fd5af2cc6435ca5e6a16b231614bdaea\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.aQwXhhRfoxcH57l5haazA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxOS42OTUwNDQ0NzI2ODE-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FC6kbRyAt1XpOAzSFF9JKKw--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz03ODc7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2Ffd5af2cc6435ca5e6a16b231614bdaea&h=4e9f0bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然 Meghan 與哈里已經決定正式退下王室身份，但有關兩人的新聞和消息仍然持續更新。而兩人早前接受荷里活名嘴Oprah 的訪問即將播出，據指長達2小時的訪問中，Meghan與哈里會大談王室生活。不過訪問未出街，已經有更勁爆的消息傳出，有指Meghan 曾經因為霸凌和恐嚇王室工作人員被投訴，Meghan則公開反指白金漢宮抹黑自己，哈利夫婦與王室公開反面對決，看來關係正式決裂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/amI8KkGQtDx_VrHYcrvn.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTEwMTQuNTEyMTk1MTIxOTUxMg--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/6j4kjMb.A3B732q6DQ26rg--~B/aD01OTA7dz00MTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/f8f326aa950e9c8c46f6b8ca367506fe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FamI8KkGQtDx_VrHYcrvn.Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTEwMTQuNTEyMTk1MTIxOTUxMg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6j4kjMb.A3B732q6DQ26rg--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz00MTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2Ff8f326aa950e9c8c46f6b8ca367506fe&h=a7abe42c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前《泰晤士報》登出文章，指控Meghan因為霸凌、恐嚇王室的工作人員而被投訴，當中更指有員工被她嚇哭，甚至被趕出門。報道甚至公開了工作人員的投訴郵件，當中提到她將兩個私人助理趕走，並「在情感上對人進行傷害和操縰」，又形容Meghan是令人反感的霸凌者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ijLvAqq0YIggyOF797SNsQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxOS42OTUwNDQ0NzI2ODE-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/s1lkKcdEo36cEge9Q.dOHA--~B/aD01OTA7dz03ODc7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/83f1d3e916075d59d4ab4a4c03e43db5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FijLvAqq0YIggyOF797SNsQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxOS42OTUwNDQ0NzI2ODE-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fs1lkKcdEo36cEge9Q.dOHA--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz03ODc7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2F83f1d3e916075d59d4ab4a4c03e43db5&h=285f0288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據指王室在接到投訴時，曾經告誡哈利，指若工作人員得到不好的待遇，將會造成大問題，但Meghan卻回應：「溺愛其他人不是我的工作。」<br />\n<br />\n有指因為哈里夫婦部分工作人員是與威廉王子一家共用的，因此Meghan對工作人員的態度，令到威廉王子非常擔心，也因而增加了兩人之間的不和。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jiyohZX.8leRYjtr5ze_kA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2MC4xMzk4NjAxMzk4NjAy/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/q2wj6a53V4inrT93ulPO3g--~B/aD01OTA7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/6f816740c1e7ab37f26b3afb78568348\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjiyohZX.8leRYjtr5ze_kA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2MC4xMzk4NjAxMzk4NjAy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq2wj6a53V4inrT93ulPO3g--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2F6f816740c1e7ab37f26b3afb78568348&h=11728121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMeghan 之後否認指控，又指摘白金漢宮借報紙抹黑她，甚至形容《泰晤士報》被王室利用，予頭直指英女王。她又透過律師表示，Meghan 自己曾經也是一個被霸凌者，因此致力支持經歷痛苦的人，努力樹立榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/R7EgFQF.4vVQD8vNx2RV4Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/rDFG6aagc5ENu4ulQ7rQ_A--~B/aD01OTA7dz04ODU7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/03f9077e4eed823b9285010ba45f6670\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FR7EgFQF.4vVQD8vNx2RV4Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrDFG6aagc5ENu4ulQ7rQ_A--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz04ODU7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2F03f9077e4eed823b9285010ba45f6670&h=07f9060a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她又透過律師表示，工作人員都與Meghan 相處融洽，例如2019年她自己出錢請所有工作人員吃雪糕，大家都形容這是世界上最快樂的工作日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kdGb_bn2ncmfyj6xFTctoQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc5MS4wNjE0NTI1MTM5NjY1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/sgwxC.GrLe4LgmKFi8PJEw--~B/aD01OTA7dz03MTY7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/6b8d5f174430f7f76074d300e0a710d5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkdGb_bn2ncmfyj6xFTctoQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc5MS4wNjE0NTI1MTM5NjY1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsgwxC.GrLe4LgmKFi8PJEw--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz03MTY7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2F6b8d5f174430f7f76074d300e0a710d5&h=844f2147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件傳出後，王室立即下令調查有關指控，又表示不會容忍任何職場的霸凌行為。王室突然高調回應，與以往喜愛息事寧人的作風完全不同，讓人吃驚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LEsXpg.FlvcAHrKtz4BUuA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1OC4yMzI5MzE3MjY5MDc2/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/M4IxtVUxP6qjNSegrf1b5Q--~B/aD01OTA7dz03NDc7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/327cb801f7fdc2a7e3f2582a2876e033\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLEsXpg.FlvcAHrKtz4BUuA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1OC4yMzI5MzE3MjY5MDc2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FM4IxtVUxP6qjNSegrf1b5Q--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz03NDc7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2F327cb801f7fdc2a7e3f2582a2876e033&h=8f23c9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民形容王室此舉全因為Meghan與哈利即將播出，怕她會於節目中提到太多敏感話題。<br />\n<br />\n而節目日前又再釋出新預告，其中梅根指王室「長期對我們進行假宣傳，我們要將真相說出來。」、「既然王室散播謠言，不要忘想我們會沉默。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2ZCmACX8usow7SNq0KKLZQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2NS40MDU0MDU0MDU0MDU0/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/S0CR4xsctRI5PE_v7DnxDQ--~B/aD01OTA7dz03NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/elle.hk/dd656801bba2e16aea8cf1ed42e27268\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2ZCmACX8usow7SNq0KKLZQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2NS40MDU0MDU0MDU0MDU0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FS0CR4xsctRI5PE_v7DnxDQ--~B%2FaD01OTA7dz03NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Felle.hk%2Fdd656801bba2e16aea8cf1ed42e27268&h=0118513e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有形容3月7日節目播出時，將會是哈利夫婦對王室的最大報復，但既然王室已經下令調查霸凌的指控，則變成兩邊的互相斯殺！"},{"pid":"31e94877ce702620601fc1ce5373c0f48bfecb27","tid":2435155,"uid":155682,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"cheap到請食雪糕都好似好大恩惠咁....."},{"pid":"52c1bf6124339928dc5287dfcdea8c24b135134d","tid":2435155,"uid":38143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:53:01.000Z","msg":"食個雪糕已經係最值得拎出黎講既野...."},{"pid":"e7356101c97f1390b47ba7a88c010e73a902082d","tid":2435155,"uid":197857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"成個西女人格收唔埋 好難唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c9118b762a032146acfe97afa4dc699c459cd9","tid":2435155,"uid":30145,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"<code>2019年她自己出錢請所有工作人員吃雪糕，大家都形容這是世界上最快樂的工作日。</code><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><stron